text: Miss Malaysia Universe 2009 is the 47th edition of the Miss Universe Malaysia pageant which was held at the Royale Chulan Hotel, Kuala Lumpur on May 30, 2009 where the reigning winner Levy Li of Terengganu crowned her successor Joannabelle Ng from Sabah at the end of the event. ==Results== {| class="wikitable sortable" style="font-size: 90%;" !width="200" style="background-color:#787878;color:#FFFFFF;"|Final Results !width="325" style="background-color:#787878;color:#FFFFFF;"|Contestants |- |Miss Universe Malaysia 2009 | * ' - Joannabelle Ng' |- |1st Runner-Up | * ' - Cassandra Patrick |- |2nd Runner-Up | * ' - Claudia Sibert |- |Top 5 | * ' - Amellia Liew * ' - Sonia Menon |- |Top 8 | * ' - Chantelle Chuah * ' - Jenny Chong * ' - Christy Yeoh |} ==Special awards== {| class="wikitable sortable" style="font-size: 90%;" !width="250" style="background- color:#787878;color:#FFFFFF;"|Awards !width="270" style="background- color:#787878;color:#FFFFFF;"|Contestants |- | Miss Photogenic | *' - Cassandra Patrick |- | Best in Swimsuit | *' - Robyna Hon |- | Audience Favorite | *' - Joannabelle Ng |- | Miss TANGS Most Fashionable | *' - Chantelle Chuah |- | Miss Adonis | *' - Jenny Chong |- | Miss Friendship | *' - Joannabelle Ng |- | Miss Online Favorite | *' - Charlene Yeong |- |} ==Crossovers == Contestants who previously competed/appeared at other national beauty pageants: ;Miss Tourism Queen International 2009 * 2009 - Cassandra Patrick (Top 20) == References == Category:2009 in Malaysia Category:2009 beauty pageants 2009
